  - Hover effects with smooth transitions
  - Clear visual indication of active dataset
\n**Enhanced Chart Creation Workflow:**
- **'Choose Your Dataset' Option:**
  - Located directly below the'Create Chart' button or section
  - Dropdown menu displaying all available datasets in the current project
  - Shows dataset name, row count, and column count for each option
  - Allows users to select which dataset to use for creating the current chart
  - Selected dataset applies only to the chart being created, not globally
  - Enables working with multiple datasets simultaneously in the same visualization workspace
  - Default selection is the currently active dataset from the top-level dataset selector

- **Multi-Dataset Chart Creation:**
  - Users can create charts from different datasets without switching the global dataset selection
  - Each chart retains its source dataset information
  - Chart editing preserves the original dataset selection
