    - Predefined range options (Top 10, Bottom 10, Above average, Below average)\n  - Apply filters globally: All charts in dashboard update based on selected filters
  - Filter dependencies: Configure cascading filters where one filter affects another
  - Clear filters option: Reset all filters to default state with single click
  - Save filter presets for quick access to common filter combinations

- **Cross-Chart Interactivity:**
