- **Statistics Cards** (Reference: image.png showing workspace statistics):
  - **Total Projects Done**: Count of all saved projects in Previous Projects section
  - **Total Charts Created**: Count of all charts created across all projects
  - **ML Models Trained**: Count of all machine learning models trained across all projects
  - **Rows in Dataset**: Total number of rows in currently active dataset
  - **Columns in Dataset**: Total number of columns in currently active dataset
  - **Dataset Name**: Display name of currently active dataset
\n- **Card Design**:
  - Large, bold numeric values prominently displayed
  - Clear descriptive labels below each number
  - Dark background with purple/teal accent colors
  - Consistent card sizing and spacing
  - Hover effects with subtle glow
